<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='843000' id='t-843000'>The world is just so tasty.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='845000' id='t-845000'>We think we'll go to a museum; that's where all the tastes are.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='847000' id='t-847000'>No, they're all out there.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='849000' id='t-849000'>So, this is, like, in front of the Eiffel Tower, really,</span>
