<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='853000' id='t-853000'>This I found, where nature had made a picture for me.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='855000' id='t-855000'>This is a perfect 90-degree angle by nature.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='857000' id='t-857000'>In this strange moment where, like, these things kind of appeared.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='860000' id='t-860000'>We all are creative people.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='862000' id='t-862000'>We have this gene defect in our mind.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='865000' id='t-865000'>We can't help but stop, right? This feeling's a wonderful thing.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='868000' id='t-868000'>It's the forever-always-on museum.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='871000' id='t-871000'>This is from the Cape last year.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='873000' id='t-873000'>I discovered that I had to find the equation of art and design,</span>
