<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='879000' id='t-879000'>It's everywhere on the beach, I discovered.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='881000' id='t-881000'>I began to collect every instance of circle-triangle-square.</span>
