<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='923000' id='t-923000'>But I discovered in the French word raison d'être.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='926000' id='t-926000'>I was, like, aha, wait a second.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='928000' id='t-928000'>And there RISD appeared.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='931000' id='t-931000'>And so I realized it was O.K. to go.</span>
